<driver id="driver/ppmtomd">
  <name>ppmtomd</name>
  <url>http://www.stevens-bradfield.com/ppmtomd/</url>
  <thirdpartysupplied />
  <execution>
    <filter />
    <prototype>gs -q -dNOPAUSE -dBATCH -dPARANOIDSAFER -sDEVICE=ppmraw -sOutputFile=-%A%B -informat Colour%C</prototype>
  </execution>
  <comments>
    <en>

    This driver works on the MicroDry thermal transfer printers: The
    Alps MD series, the Citizen printiva series, and the Okidata DP
    series. It is the successor of the &quot;ppmtocpva&quot;
    driver.&lt;p&gt;

    Note that the &quot;&lt;tt&gt;-autoshift&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; feature
    is broken in the versions 1.0.2 and older. This is fixed in
    1.0.3.&lt;p&gt;

    From version 1.1 on the Dye Sublimation mode is fully
    supported. The VPhoto mode and VPhoto primer support are available
    from version 1.3 on.&lt;p&gt;

  </en>
  </comments>
